snippet.title: A Bug's Life Trailer 1999
snippet.description:
A Bug's Life Trailer 1999

Official Content From Def Squad

Follow the exploits of Flik, and help defend his home from the invading grasshoppers. Help Flik solve puzzels as he explores the world around him. This game is great for the kids.
Platforms: Sony PlayStation, Nintendo 64
